thread.title: BRIEF-Hangzhou Tianmushan Pharmaceutical Enterprise sees FY 2017 net profit up 1,872 pct to 2,364 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Hangzhou Tianmushan Pharmaceutical Enterprise sees FY 2017 net profit up 1,872 pct to 2,364 pct

organizations.name: hangzhou tianmushan pharmaceutical enterprise co ltd

text:
Feb 1(Reuters) - Hangzhou Tianmushan Pharmaceutical Enterprise Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 1,872 percent to 2,364 percent, or to be 24 million yuan to 30 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 1.2 million yuan
* The reasons for the forecast are production recovery and assets disposal Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/KB7KhH Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
